---
title: Plant-Based Mince & Veggie Stir-Fry with Udon Noodles & Parsley
description: Soothing noodles are wrapping up all the flavours of sweet and soy plant-based mince to transform into a vibrant stir-fry. You don’t want to miss the incredible combo of sweet chilli sauce paired with a rich Korean stir-fry sauce - this bowl is going to be a veggie fan-fave for sure.
